divs: Sighting DetailsWent outside to let dogs out looked up at moon saw a bright glowing object came back inside house got iPhone video taped a object making turns and moves conventional fixed wing aircraft could not do these manuvers I have two clips on tape in my phone not sure how to send it to you the object was high altitude( not sure )how high south into York county I beleive the video is time stamped my wife who is skeptacle well educated can't explain this I had difficulty sleeping sincerely, Dean Teeter
